---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Responsible Disclosure - ByteLite"
  description="ByteLite's responsible disclosure policy for security researchers and ethical hackers."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Responsible Disclosure Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          ByteLite values the security community and believes that responsible disclosure of security 
          vulnerabilities helps us ensure the security and privacy of our users.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Scope</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          This policy applies to any vulnerabilities discovered in:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-300">
          <li>ByteLite compression technology</li>
          <li>Deep Kore systems and infrastructure</li>
          <li>Our websites and web applications</li>
          <li>Our APIs and backend services</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">How to Report</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          If you believe you've found a security vulnerability, please email us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-center my-6">
          <a href="mailto:security@thebytelite.com" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-xl font-mono">
            security@thebytelite.com
          </a>
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What to Include</h2>
        <ul class="text-gray-300">
          <li>Description of the vulnerability</li>
          <li>Steps to reproduce the issue</li>
          <li>Potential impact</li>
          <li>Any proof-of-concept code</li>
          <li>Your contact information</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
        <ul class="text-gray-300">
          <li>We will acknowledge receipt within 48 hours</li>
          <li>We will provide an initial assessment within 7 days</li>
          <li>We will keep you informed about our progress</li>
          <li>We will credit you (if desired) when the issue is resolved</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Please Don't</h2>
        <ul class="text-gray-300">
          <li>Access or modify user data without permission</li>
          <li>Perform actions that could harm our services or users</li>
          <li>Publicly disclose the issue before we've addressed it</li>
          <li>Demand compensation or rewards</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Recognition</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          We appreciate the security community's efforts in helping us maintain the highest security standards. 
          With your permission, we'll acknowledge your contribution in our security hall of fame.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cyan-400">Legal Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We will not pursue legal action against security researchers who:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
            <li>Follow this responsible disclosure policy</li>
            <li>Act in good faith</li>
            <li>Do not cause harm to our systems or users</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    color: #E0E0E0;
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
</style>